WEBVTT

01:35.900 --> 01:40.980
=Love Beyond the Grave=
(Adapted from the novel by Li Qingran)

01:41.260 --> 01:43.990
=Episode 26=

01:53.340 --> 01:54.580
Milady, it's raining.

01:54.990 --> 01:56.030
Wait here and take shelter.

01:56.030 --> 01:57.060
I'll go get the carriage.

02:01.390 --> 02:02.500
It's you.

02:03.380 --> 02:05.700
(Yueran Fragrance)

02:05.700 --> 02:07.060
It's another rainy day.

02:08.140 --> 02:09.270
And I've met you again.

02:14.420 --> 02:15.950
I'm Duan Jingyuan.

02:17.270 --> 02:18.350
Mister,

02:19.510 --> 02:20.830
who are you?

02:28.550 --> 02:29.390
Greetings, Miss Duan.

02:30.180 --> 02:31.420
I'm from a humble family

02:31.700 --> 02:32.950
and I'm just a nobody.

02:34.070 --> 02:35.140
My name is Fang Ji,

02:35.990 --> 02:36.830
courtesy name Xianye.

02:43.790 --> 02:46.140
Fang Xianye?

02:50.460 --> 02:51.420
You...

02:51.420 --> 02:53.790
You're the one who goes

02:53.790 --> 02:55.510
against my father and my third brother?

02:56.950 --> 02:57.790
I...

03:16.460 --> 03:17.830
I've heard you are

03:18.580 --> 03:20.070
the top scholar of Nandu.

03:20.510 --> 03:22.110
Most of the finest essays of this era

03:22.270 --> 03:23.700
are authored by you.

03:25.300 --> 03:26.270
I've long heard of you.

03:35.950 --> 03:37.110
You flatter me, Miss Duan.

03:37.700 --> 03:39.550
My essays may shake the world...

03:39.740 --> 03:41.390
My essays may shake the world...

03:41.990 --> 03:43.140
But that's just empty talk.

03:43.300 --> 03:44.740
But that's just empty talk.

03:58.660 --> 04:01.300
(Be worthy of the world...)

04:03.300 --> 04:05.140
(Bravery is the bone of heroism.)
Your essay

04:05.140 --> 04:07.230
has always been the best.

04:07.460 --> 04:09.790
(That's the spirit of heroism.)
You'll be the top scholar.

04:22.030 --> 04:23.740
Why do you talk like my brother?

04:27.030 --> 04:28.380
General Duan is of noble birth.

04:29.060 --> 04:30.420
I can't compare to him.

04:34.740 --> 04:35.740
How hypocritical.

04:45.670 --> 04:47.590
Why is it still raining?

04:54.670 --> 04:55.620
You don't need...

05:01.060 --> 05:01.900
Why is there

05:02.180 --> 05:03.710
such a deep scar on your hand?

05:04.940 --> 05:06.230
On my way to the Capital,

05:06.230 --> 05:07.150
I encountered bandits

05:07.420 --> 05:08.550
and nearly lost my life.

05:09.300 --> 05:11.260
Luckily, Duke Pei saved me
and took me in.

05:12.150 --> 05:13.300
I got this scar

05:13.300 --> 05:14.140
at that time.

05:15.180 --> 05:16.110
Oh, I see.

05:18.180 --> 05:19.740
It's not safe around here.

05:20.740 --> 05:21.740
My third brother

05:22.940 --> 05:24.180
encountered bandits too.

05:32.940 --> 05:35.230
(No wonder he works for Duke Pei.)

05:36.550 --> 05:38.230
(So this is the reason.)

05:40.060 --> 05:41.590
(After all, Duke Pei)

05:41.590 --> 05:42.740
(is the most terrible man.)

05:45.990 --> 05:47.030
Miss Duan,

05:49.150 --> 05:50.990
are you going to hold me forever?

06:07.590 --> 06:08.430
I've heard

06:09.940 --> 06:11.260
you have a feud with my family.

06:12.380 --> 06:13.300
Is that true?

06:15.260 --> 06:16.380
I'm an ordinary man.

06:16.670 --> 06:17.510
Before my success,

06:17.740 --> 06:18.740
I hadn't even met

06:18.740 --> 06:20.380
your father or brother.

06:30.710 --> 06:32.300
(This man)

06:32.860 --> 06:34.420
(isn't as annoying)

06:34.420 --> 06:35.470
(as I imagined.)

06:44.180 --> 06:48.980
(Lotusborn Pavilion)

07:02.790 --> 07:03.670
Everything's ready.

07:04.300 --> 07:05.420
I'll just wait

07:05.420 --> 07:07.030
for Great Ancestor's last material.

07:16.910 --> 07:18.230
You look too old in this outfit.

07:18.470 --> 07:19.310
Don't wear it again.

07:21.550 --> 07:22.500
I'm the Prophet.

07:25.260 --> 07:26.110
A prophet wears this.

07:28.790 --> 07:29.860
This is what you asked for.

07:35.300 --> 07:36.140
Great Ancestor,

07:36.150 --> 07:37.260
this isn't enough.

07:37.260 --> 07:38.470
Why did you get so little?

07:41.710 --> 07:42.550
Oh, Great Ancestor.

07:43.620 --> 07:45.380
Finding this stuff isn't easy.

07:45.670 --> 07:46.710
No rush.

07:49.420 --> 07:50.260
Great Ancestor,

07:50.710 --> 07:52.260
I've got you a room

07:52.260 --> 07:53.740
with a wonderful view.

07:53.940 --> 07:56.110
You can overlook the entire city

07:56.300 --> 07:58.820
and enjoy all the breathtaking views.

07:59.470 --> 08:01.260
Make yourself at home

08:01.260 --> 08:02.470
until the artifact is done.

08:03.420 --> 08:04.260
No need.

08:05.380 --> 08:06.350
I have somewhere to stay.

08:09.030 --> 08:09.870
Your Lordship,

08:10.030 --> 08:10.990
we've searched the Void,

08:11.180 --> 08:12.740
but haven't found Bai Sanxing.

08:17.470 --> 08:18.670
Keep searching.

08:18.860 --> 08:19.700
Yes.

08:26.230 --> 08:27.260
One day,

08:28.260 --> 08:29.710
you will die

08:30.260 --> 08:31.860
by the hand of your beloved.

08:36.710 --> 08:38.070
(Hide in the Mortal World)

08:38.590 --> 08:40.190
(and collect spirit aura.)

09:27.230 --> 09:28.110
Assassin!

09:28.110 --> 09:29.020
Protect Mr. Fang!

10:08.590 --> 10:09.430
Catch the assassin!

10:09.660 --> 10:10.500
Protect Mr. Fang!

10:10.510 --> 10:12.190
- Yes!
- Yes!

10:17.590 --> 10:18.430
No need to pursue.

10:20.470 --> 10:21.400
On Duke Pei's orders,

10:21.400 --> 10:22.260
we've come to get you.

10:22.260 --> 10:23.110
Sorry for all that.

10:23.110 --> 10:23.990
Please forgive us.

10:24.430 --> 10:25.270
That was unexpected.

10:25.540 --> 10:26.380
Let's head back now.

10:26.740 --> 10:27.860
Don't hold up our plans.

10:28.590 --> 10:29.430
- Yes.
- Yes.

10:29.430 --> 10:35.140
(Yuzao Pleasure House)

10:43.470 --> 10:44.660
Nice.

11:12.830 --> 11:13.670
Hi, Ying.

11:14.740 --> 11:16.020
The new dish today tastes good.

11:16.500 --> 11:17.380
Then enjoy your meal.

11:18.380 --> 11:19.220
Take your time.

11:21.430 --> 11:22.950
Young Master Xu, it's been so long

11:22.950 --> 11:23.900
since you returned.

11:24.070 --> 11:25.380
Have you forgotten us?

11:25.800 --> 11:26.680
Whatever happens,

11:26.680 --> 11:27.950
I'll never forget you, Luoxian.

11:28.230 --> 11:29.110
Come with me, please.

11:34.430 --> 11:35.590
Let's go to the private room.

11:35.590 --> 11:36.430
All right.

11:36.780 --> 11:38.070
I'll have a good drink with you.

11:47.380 --> 11:50.900
(Luoxian, Yuzao Pleasure House)

11:50.900 --> 11:51.740
This floor is taken.

11:52.020 --> 11:52.860
Keep people away.

11:53.140 --> 11:54.140
Yes, Young Master Xu.

12:23.900 --> 12:25.380
Your zither skills

12:25.830 --> 12:26.990
still need improvement.

12:30.070 --> 12:32.110
If you can't appreciate my music,

12:32.900 --> 12:34.500
I happen to have

12:35.500 --> 12:36.470
some martial arts.

12:40.350 --> 12:41.190
There's no point.

12:41.830 --> 12:42.780
You can't beat me.

12:43.580 --> 12:44.420
Any damage in here

12:44.430 --> 12:45.470
has to be fixed.

12:48.660 --> 12:49.950
Your father will pay, anyway.

12:51.780 --> 12:52.990
This is a place of business.

12:53.190 --> 12:54.230
Is this what you wear?

12:57.260 --> 12:58.140
Young Master,

12:58.780 --> 13:00.540
I'm just back from a mission.

13:00.540 --> 13:01.660
I was almost exhausted.

13:02.620 --> 13:04.260
And it's past midnight.

13:04.710 --> 13:05.950
If I weren't waiting for you,

13:06.380 --> 13:07.500
I would have gone to bed.

13:08.430 --> 13:09.270
You worked hard.

13:10.710 --> 13:11.590
How did it go?

13:12.990 --> 13:14.470
You may doubt my zither skills,

13:14.780 --> 13:16.230
but you can't doubt my capability.

13:17.230 --> 13:18.990
My assassination was successful.

13:19.950 --> 13:21.230
But I don't understand.

13:21.990 --> 13:23.310
You sent me to assassinate him,

13:23.540 --> 13:24.660
but not to kill him.

13:25.540 --> 13:26.380
Why?

13:40.260 --> 13:41.190
Mr. Fang, in you go.

13:42.860 --> 13:43.700
Mentor.

13:52.620 --> 13:53.590
How did you get injured?

13:54.020 --> 13:55.020
Go get the medicine kit.

13:55.380 --> 13:56.580
- Yes.
- It's nothing.

14:02.350 --> 14:03.660
How did you get injured so badly?

14:16.430 --> 14:17.830
How could I trouble you, Mentor?

14:25.310 --> 14:26.260
In the future,

14:26.260 --> 14:27.780
I'll give you more guards.

14:28.660 --> 14:30.070
You must not travel alone again

14:30.430 --> 14:31.350
like you did today.

14:32.260 --> 14:33.100
Oh.

14:33.310 --> 14:35.380
Is there any lead on the assassin?

14:37.500 --> 14:38.950
Some people want me dead

14:39.660 --> 14:40.500
simply because

14:40.500 --> 14:41.860
I'm in their way.

14:47.950 --> 14:48.860
It seems Chancellor Du

14:49.710 --> 14:51.110
has been too impatient.

14:58.950 --> 14:59.950
He's being impatient

15:00.660 --> 15:02.260
just because our military power

15:02.710 --> 15:04.110
completely rests with you.

15:05.140 --> 15:06.620
Imperial Guard Commander Meng Qiaoyan,

15:06.620 --> 15:08.190
involved in the Southwest rebellion,

15:08.660 --> 15:09.950
was Du's strongest force

15:09.950 --> 15:10.900
in the army.

15:11.590 --> 15:12.500
Later, Meng Qiaoyan

15:12.500 --> 15:14.110
chose to step back from court disputes.

15:14.540 --> 15:15.990
Then Chancellor Du started

15:15.990 --> 15:16.860
to cultivate Duan Xu.

15:18.660 --> 15:19.500
This time,

15:20.740 --> 15:22.260
Duan Xu repelled the Chong Army.

15:23.020 --> 15:25.190
Chancellor Du wanted
to divide the military power.

15:25.620 --> 15:26.590
Unexpectedly, His Majesty

15:27.310 --> 15:29.230
turned Duan Xu into a civil official.

15:29.950 --> 15:31.470
Chancellor Du's only hope

15:31.660 --> 15:32.660
failed as well.

15:33.350 --> 15:35.110
So he won't just wait for his doom.

15:35.620 --> 15:36.780
The assassination today

15:37.380 --> 15:38.350
is also a warning.

15:39.140 --> 15:40.310
He must have further schemes.

15:53.380 --> 15:54.310
Put it back.

16:01.860 --> 16:02.990
You're right.

16:03.950 --> 16:05.860
Ever since Duan Xu returned,

16:06.380 --> 16:09.310
Duan Chengzhang has been
secretly arranging a marriage for him.

16:10.590 --> 16:11.500
Wang Suyi, the 3rd child

16:11.500 --> 16:12.780
of Minister Wang of Revenue,

16:13.500 --> 16:14.950
Lu Changling, the 5th child

16:15.110 --> 16:15.950
of Academician Lu,

16:16.380 --> 16:17.950
and Xie Qiuyan, the 4th child

16:18.230 --> 16:19.110
of Prince Xie,

16:19.710 --> 16:20.550
are all on the list.

16:21.660 --> 16:23.990
Minister Wang holds real power
in the Minister of Revenue.

16:24.470 --> 16:25.900
Academician Lu is the Imperial Tutor,

16:26.110 --> 16:27.430
deeply trusted by His Majesty.

16:28.110 --> 16:30.020
Prince Xie is an aristocrat.

16:30.740 --> 16:31.860
These men

16:31.860 --> 16:32.950
have always been righteous.

16:33.830 --> 16:35.660
The support from any one of them

16:35.950 --> 16:37.190
will have huge influence.

16:37.740 --> 16:39.230
Chancellor Du still backs Duan Xu.

16:40.190 --> 16:41.030
Your Lordship,

16:41.350 --> 16:43.070
shall we press our advantage?

16:44.780 --> 16:45.620
The fish has bitten.

16:55.860 --> 16:56.900
I specially had my men

16:57.140 --> 16:58.500
build a fish pond here.

16:59.350 --> 17:00.430
So I can enjoy

17:00.740 --> 17:02.380
the joy of fishing without leaving home.

17:05.430 --> 17:06.670
Now I've got the first carp.

17:06.990 --> 17:07.950
It's a sign for action.

17:08.740 --> 17:09.630
Then please go

17:10.390 --> 17:11.820
to the 5th Prince's Mansion.

17:12.710 --> 17:13.780
After all,

17:14.300 --> 17:15.870
he's old enough to get married.

17:18.390 --> 17:19.230
Yes.

17:23.430 --> 17:24.300
Here's what you want,

17:24.580 --> 17:25.710
information about Wang Suyi.

17:26.300 --> 17:27.140
Also,

17:27.540 --> 17:28.780
a tip just came in.

17:29.260 --> 17:30.630
After Fang Xianye was attacked,

17:30.950 --> 17:32.630
he headed straight to the 5th Prince's.

17:33.780 --> 17:34.620
As you expected,

17:34.950 --> 17:36.230
Duke Pei wants the 5th Prince,

17:36.230 --> 17:37.670
who is of marriageable age,

17:37.820 --> 17:38.710
to steal your bride.

17:40.020 --> 17:41.340
But I'm confused.

17:41.870 --> 17:43.300
Why do you get yourself

17:43.710 --> 17:44.990
a rival in love?

17:50.020 --> 17:51.300
The 5th Prince is the right age.

17:53.300 --> 17:54.500
He'll get married.

17:55.670 --> 17:56.580
I'm not getting myself

17:56.580 --> 17:57.430
a rival in love,

17:57.870 --> 17:59.500
but eliminating a real rival.

18:01.340 --> 18:02.180
Through contrast,

18:02.910 --> 18:04.150
my value will be clearer,

18:04.870 --> 18:05.710
won't it?

18:10.500 --> 18:11.340
Fine.

18:12.630 --> 18:13.500
Oh,

18:13.500 --> 18:15.630
a rumor is going around in Nandu

18:15.630 --> 18:16.990
that Young Master Xu loafs

18:16.990 --> 18:17.830
and fools around.

18:18.060 --> 18:19.300
Are you really getting married?

18:20.340 --> 18:21.230
Soon, you'll know

18:21.990 --> 18:23.020
what I'm going to do.

18:27.500 --> 18:28.710
Aren't you going downstairs?

18:29.300 --> 18:30.260
Many people are waiting.

18:30.710 --> 18:32.740
Why would I need to play music myself?

18:33.500 --> 18:34.540
Even if my fingers

18:34.540 --> 18:35.500
were swollen,

18:35.500 --> 18:36.500
they wouldn't understand.

18:37.430 --> 18:38.710
A new top beauty is here today.

18:38.990 --> 18:40.060
Otherwise,

18:40.060 --> 18:41.260
I wouldn't have time for you.

18:41.820 --> 18:42.660
I'd have been asleep.

18:43.060 --> 18:44.230
Then go to sleep.

18:49.870 --> 18:51.060
When can I go back?

18:53.500 --> 18:54.340
Soon.

18:54.470 --> 18:55.870
You said the same thing last time.

18:57.950 --> 18:59.060
I'll keep my word this time.

19:33.470 --> 19:34.670
Is this the new top beauty?

19:35.300 --> 19:36.140
Quite impressive.

19:36.340 --> 19:37.190
Exactly.

19:37.190 --> 19:38.820
This top beauty is quite special.

19:39.100 --> 19:40.470
She loves to hear stories.

20:11.660 --> 20:13.900
(5th Prince's Mansion)

20:19.990 --> 20:21.990
Your Highness,
Mr. Fang is here to see you.

20:25.430 --> 20:26.270
Your Highness?

20:26.470 --> 20:27.540
Mr. Fang is here.

20:31.390 --> 20:32.230
Come in.

20:37.630 --> 20:39.710
Your Highness,
Mr. Fang is here to see you.

20:53.190 --> 20:54.030
Your Highness.

20:54.580 --> 20:55.420
Come over.

21:12.540 --> 21:13.380
Your Highness.

21:22.500 --> 21:23.340
Your Highness?

21:47.700 --> 21:51.340
(Consort Yu)

22:02.990 --> 22:03.910
Stop playing.

22:03.910 --> 22:04.780
Get up now.

22:10.630 --> 22:12.230
You won't miss out on the treasures.

22:12.540 --> 22:13.470
Why aren't you up yet?

22:17.230 --> 22:18.390
You don't let me out, do you?

22:19.190 --> 22:20.470
Why can't I just play?

22:21.020 --> 22:22.470
Fang Xianye is here.

22:23.150 --> 22:24.740
(Han Mingxuan, 5th Prince)
Who's that?

22:24.740 --> 22:25.780
Why is he here?

22:27.630 --> 22:28.470
Fang Xianye

22:28.470 --> 22:30.260
is Duke Pei's close confidant.

22:31.300 --> 22:32.990
He came in person so late.

22:33.500 --> 22:35.060
He must have something important to say.

22:37.390 --> 22:38.500
That's your business.

22:39.190 --> 22:40.060
None of my business.

22:41.990 --> 22:42.830
Don't forget.

22:43.150 --> 22:44.020
Your cooperation

22:44.020 --> 22:45.150
with every move we make

22:45.150 --> 22:46.260
is the only way

22:46.260 --> 22:47.340
to keep things as they are.

22:50.230 --> 22:52.300
If you no longer want a great life,

22:53.230 --> 22:54.870
try to refuse me.

22:59.020 --> 22:59.860
Fine.

23:01.820 --> 23:02.710
I'll just go

23:02.710 --> 23:04.100
and see that man.

23:21.050 --> 23:21.890
Greetings,

23:21.910 --> 23:23.040
Your Highness

23:23.150 --> 23:23.990
and Your Grace.

23:24.430 --> 23:25.870
No need for such formality, Mr. Fang.

23:26.060 --> 23:26.900
Take a seat.

23:29.260 --> 23:30.540
How many times have I told you?

23:31.340 --> 23:32.260
I can't eat this thing

23:32.260 --> 23:33.100
and it's ugly too.

23:33.370 --> 23:34.210
Just display

23:34.230 --> 23:35.070
the Seven Seas Dragon Pearl.

23:38.630 --> 23:39.710
What is your purpose?

23:40.540 --> 23:41.990
Duke Pei has a message.

23:42.580 --> 23:43.710
Your Highness

23:43.710 --> 23:44.950
is old enough to get married.

23:46.100 --> 23:47.670
Did he send you

23:47.950 --> 23:48.910
because he had

23:48.910 --> 23:50.060
candidates for my son?

23:58.100 --> 23:58.940
(Wang Suyi)

23:58.950 --> 23:59.790
(Changling, Qiuyan)

24:06.470 --> 24:07.310
Son.

24:11.870 --> 24:12.870
So Duke Pei wants me

24:12.870 --> 24:14.100
to marry the three of them.

24:16.780 --> 24:17.620
Then get prepared.

24:17.990 --> 24:19.670
I'm getting married tomorrow.

24:27.260 --> 24:29.340
Their fathers are important officials

24:29.470 --> 24:30.540
who have been neutral.

24:30.780 --> 24:32.340
Marrying a prince will get them involved

24:32.580 --> 24:34.500
in the fight for the throne.

24:34.670 --> 24:36.260
How would they agree easily?

24:36.360 --> 24:37.220
Your Grace,

24:37.230 --> 24:39.150
you just follow Duke Pei's instructions.

24:39.630 --> 24:41.470
Then he'll spare no effort

24:41.470 --> 24:42.500
to support your son.

24:43.260 --> 24:44.740
Since the message is delivered,

24:45.100 --> 24:46.060
I'll take my leave.

24:46.710 --> 24:47.580
Mr. Fang.

24:50.870 --> 24:52.470
Please tell Duke Pei.

24:53.300 --> 24:54.340
Hope he won't forget

24:54.340 --> 24:56.100
his promise to my son and me.

24:58.670 --> 24:59.580
I'll tell him.

25:50.940 --> 25:54.260
(Yuzao Pleasure House)

26:13.340 --> 26:14.180
Wine.

26:15.060 --> 26:16.340
I want wine.

26:16.470 --> 26:17.310
Come here.

26:17.910 --> 26:19.190
The new top beauty

26:19.500 --> 26:20.990
wants to hear stories, doesn't she?

26:21.430 --> 26:22.270
What...

26:22.580 --> 26:23.710
What are they doing here?

26:24.950 --> 26:25.820
Sir,

26:25.820 --> 26:26.670
you have no idea.

26:27.150 --> 26:28.740
Way too many men want

26:28.740 --> 26:29.740
to see the top beauty.

26:30.100 --> 26:31.710
So we have this new rule.

26:32.060 --> 26:33.580
No one can go up unless he finishes

26:33.580 --> 26:34.580
three jars of strong wine

26:35.060 --> 26:36.150
within about half an hour.

26:37.100 --> 26:38.580
That much?

26:38.990 --> 26:39.850
When someone's drunk,

26:39.860 --> 26:40.990
how can he tell a story?

26:41.740 --> 26:42.950
I don't know.

26:43.190 --> 26:44.300
This is her request.

26:52.630 --> 26:53.780
Then tell me.

26:54.390 --> 26:55.740
What kind of stories

26:56.190 --> 26:57.670
does she love to hear?

27:00.820 --> 27:01.990
She loves

27:02.580 --> 27:03.820
to hear stories

27:04.340 --> 27:05.340
about separated couples,

27:05.670 --> 27:06.630
mismatched sweethearts,

27:07.020 --> 27:08.230
and unattainable love.

27:09.290 --> 27:10.150
Anyway,

27:10.150 --> 27:12.390
it's about love and hatred.

27:12.390 --> 27:13.950
Waiter, another jar of wine!

27:14.340 --> 27:15.180
Be right there!

27:15.580 --> 27:16.990
Gentlemen, help yourselves.

27:19.390 --> 27:20.230
Let's go.

27:20.540 --> 27:21.670
Let's go up there.

27:22.870 --> 27:23.710
Come on.

27:47.150 --> 27:48.580
Wait. Wait for me.

27:50.430 --> 27:51.580
I'm not finished yet.

27:52.230 --> 27:53.390
My Lady,

27:53.390 --> 27:54.910
let me continue.

27:55.150 --> 27:56.230
My Lady!

27:56.430 --> 27:57.630
My Lady!

27:58.430 --> 27:59.500
My Lady!

28:00.190 --> 28:01.030
Go away.

28:01.430 --> 28:02.270
Get lost.

28:02.470 --> 28:03.310
Get out of my way.

28:03.470 --> 28:04.340
My turn.

28:04.540 --> 28:05.540
Don't jump the queue!

28:06.260 --> 28:07.100
My turn!

28:07.470 --> 28:08.310
It's my turn.

28:08.580 --> 28:09.710
He cut in line.

28:09.710 --> 28:10.550
He...

28:10.550 --> 28:11.540
- I'll go.
- How come?

28:31.230 --> 28:32.070
Miss He,

28:32.740 --> 28:33.780
I am...

28:33.780 --> 28:34.670
Welcome, sir.

28:35.670 --> 28:36.510
Take a seat.

28:38.430 --> 28:39.270
All right.

28:45.230 --> 28:46.070
Sir,

28:46.390 --> 28:47.780
please tell your story.

28:51.740 --> 28:52.580
Miss He,

28:53.500 --> 28:54.580
I'm Chen.

28:55.430 --> 28:57.100
I'm 28 years old.

28:57.740 --> 28:58.580
I live...

28:59.300 --> 29:01.470
I live in the three-sided courtyard

29:01.470 --> 29:02.740
near the city gate.

29:02.870 --> 29:03.710
Do you know that?

29:05.630 --> 29:06.470
Next.

29:07.710 --> 29:09.060
When will it be my turn?

29:10.260 --> 29:11.230
There he is.

29:15.230 --> 29:16.300
Look at him.

29:16.740 --> 29:17.870
Next!

29:18.230 --> 29:21.020
Pick me! Pick me!

29:25.150 --> 29:26.260
Welcome, sir.

29:27.780 --> 29:28.620
Take a seat.

29:39.430 --> 29:40.270
Go away.

29:40.500 --> 29:41.340
Sir,

29:42.100 --> 29:43.580
please tell your story.

30:04.100 --> 30:05.020
Here I am.

30:05.230 --> 30:06.070
Greetings, Mentor.

30:12.870 --> 30:13.710
Fang Ji,

30:14.580 --> 30:15.820
your recent essays

30:16.430 --> 30:17.630
have impressed those

30:18.020 --> 30:18.870
in the Censorate.

30:19.740 --> 30:21.390
They must have spoken favorably

30:21.780 --> 30:22.780
just for your sake.

30:26.540 --> 30:27.630
Don't be so modest.

30:29.190 --> 30:30.150
Consort Yu

30:30.540 --> 30:31.950
wants to hold a palace banquet.

30:32.780 --> 30:34.430
During that,

30:34.910 --> 30:37.540
she'll request His Majesty
for her son's marriage.

30:39.100 --> 30:40.430
So you want him

30:40.710 --> 30:41.580
to seize the advantage

30:42.430 --> 30:43.630
and steal Duan Xu's candidates,

30:44.500 --> 30:45.820
leaving him with no one to marry.

30:47.190 --> 30:49.150
You'll also go to the banquet.

30:49.470 --> 30:51.540
The 5th Prince is unpredictable.

30:53.300 --> 30:54.190
Only when you're there

30:56.950 --> 30:58.340
will I feel truly reassured.

31:01.300 --> 31:02.140
I understand.

31:08.740 --> 31:16.260
(Yuzao Pleasure House)

31:41.150 --> 31:41.990
Great Ancestor.

31:43.390 --> 31:44.780
Where are you?

31:47.780 --> 31:49.630
Your outfit looks great.

31:50.630 --> 31:51.710
I'm so bored

31:51.710 --> 31:52.820
that I act as a top beauty.

31:53.670 --> 31:54.950
This place is interesting.

31:55.910 --> 31:57.150
But people here

31:59.230 --> 32:00.390
have very few obsessions.

32:01.540 --> 32:03.430
I've just collected so little.

32:04.500 --> 32:06.260
Mortals' obsessions are the most vivid.

32:06.630 --> 32:08.300
You need strong obsessions to make

32:08.430 --> 32:09.950
the magical artifact you want.

32:10.110 --> 32:10.950
This amount

32:10.950 --> 32:11.990
is far from enough.

32:13.740 --> 32:15.060
If it goes on like this,

32:15.870 --> 32:16.820
who knows how long

32:16.820 --> 32:17.780
I'll have to wait.

32:23.780 --> 32:24.870
People in the royal palace

32:24.870 --> 32:26.150
have deep obsessions, don't they?

32:31.780 --> 32:32.620
Oh, that's right.

32:33.190 --> 32:34.390
Consort Yu will hold a banquet.

32:34.670 --> 32:35.990
We can go check out the palace.

32:36.500 --> 32:37.340
Banquet?

32:37.580 --> 32:38.990
Consort Yu will hold a banquet.

32:38.990 --> 32:40.430
Marriageable royal relatives

32:40.430 --> 32:41.390
and nobles were invited.

32:41.710 --> 32:42.910
If they fall for each other,

32:43.470 --> 32:45.060
the marriage will be settled.

32:45.190 --> 32:46.030
It's actually

32:46.230 --> 32:47.710
a wife selection for the 5th Prince.

32:49.470 --> 32:50.390
Great Ancestor,

32:50.780 --> 32:52.060
why don't we go check there?

32:52.990 --> 32:53.830
Perhaps,

32:54.580 --> 32:56.260
you'll meet the mortal you want.

33:00.820 --> 33:02.020
Good idea.

33:11.940 --> 33:18.940
(Erudite and Determined)

33:30.430 --> 33:31.540
Xu, I'm coming in.

33:32.780 --> 33:34.430
Consort Yu will hold a banquet.

33:34.580 --> 33:35.670
Father asked you to go.

33:35.920 --> 33:36.760
He also said

33:36.770 --> 33:37.870
the girls he chose for you

33:37.870 --> 33:38.710
would also be there.

33:38.720 --> 33:40.190
You should make a good impression.

33:44.990 --> 33:46.150
Father didn't tell you?

33:48.580 --> 33:49.820
Maybe he was too forgetful

33:50.150 --> 33:51.340
to bring that up.

33:54.950 --> 33:55.820
Xu,

33:57.580 --> 33:58.430
do you

33:58.440 --> 33:59.950
not like to stay in this city?

34:00.780 --> 34:01.670
I always feel

34:02.230 --> 34:03.580
something's bothering you.

34:06.950 --> 34:07.870
Don't worry about me.

34:08.430 --> 34:09.910
I have things to do here.

34:10.430 --> 34:11.950
Father may get you blind dates too.

34:31.660 --> 34:32.950
I'm having bad luck today.

34:33.540 --> 34:34.950
I can't shoot straight.

34:34.950 --> 34:35.950
You're right.

34:38.060 --> 34:39.700
Watch this. Two arrows at a time.

34:40.950 --> 34:41.990
I hit it.

34:41.990 --> 34:43.790
- Impressive.
- So steady.

34:51.460 --> 34:52.940
(Lu Changling)

34:52.950 --> 34:54.350
I heard the Duan clan also sent you

34:54.350 --> 34:55.190
a visit request.

34:55.390 --> 34:56.230
Yeah.

34:56.470 --> 34:58.100
(Xie Qiuyan)
They not only sent it to me,

34:58.470 --> 34:59.580
but also Miss Wang.

35:02.020 --> 35:04.310
(Wang Suyi)
Young Master Xu is good.

35:04.910 --> 35:06.870
He's a handsome scholar and warrior.

35:06.870 --> 35:08.180
How could anyone not like him?

35:08.390 --> 35:09.700
Sadly, he has fallen from power.

35:10.020 --> 35:11.790
Now he only has a fifth-rank sinecure

35:12.020 --> 35:13.060
and a bleak future.

35:13.660 --> 35:14.790
Now he probably needs a wife

35:15.090 --> 35:15.950
to regain power

35:15.950 --> 35:17.270
with her family's influence.

35:17.830 --> 35:19.500
I don't want to take that risk.

35:23.160 --> 35:24.030
That's Duan Xu

35:24.040 --> 35:25.310
who retook three northern cities.

35:26.470 --> 35:27.310
What a pity.

35:27.580 --> 35:28.620
He was demoted.

35:29.020 --> 35:29.870
Chancellor Du's camp

35:30.140 --> 35:31.620
has lost its influence in the army.

35:32.180 --> 35:33.180
Duan Xu's family

35:33.390 --> 35:34.660
can hardly regain power.

35:34.660 --> 35:35.790
(Wang Qi, legitimate son
of the Minister of Revenue)

35:35.790 --> 35:36.630
That's difficult.

35:39.060 --> 35:40.500
I wondered which gossipmonger

35:40.500 --> 35:41.910
was spreading rumors here.

35:42.270 --> 35:44.350
Turns out it's Minister Wang's son.

35:44.870 --> 35:45.710
Meng!

35:47.060 --> 35:47.900
He...

35:48.140 --> 35:49.310
Why did he run away?

35:51.220 --> 35:52.060
Wan?

35:52.410 --> 35:53.270
Xu,

35:53.270 --> 35:54.270
ignore those dandies.

35:59.390 --> 36:00.750
It's my father's fault.

36:01.310 --> 36:02.500
Ever since I came back here,

36:02.660 --> 36:03.580
he has been urging me

36:03.580 --> 36:04.660
to have blind dates.

36:05.020 --> 36:05.860
He also said,

36:06.350 --> 36:08.220
"Fighting in battle is useless.

36:08.390 --> 36:09.700
You'll get married anyway."

36:09.700 --> 36:11.060
I nearly slapped him.

36:11.060 --> 36:12.220
Don't listen to him, Meng.

36:12.620 --> 36:13.830
If you want to fight, then go.

36:14.060 --> 36:14.900
Maybe

36:15.100 --> 36:16.430
you'll be the first lady general

36:16.430 --> 36:17.270
of our nation.

36:17.700 --> 36:18.540
Right?

36:18.870 --> 36:20.350
I haven't thought about that yet.

36:20.990 --> 36:22.310
There's never been a lady general.

36:22.620 --> 36:23.460
Wan,

36:23.470 --> 36:24.580
maybe you'll be the first.

36:26.310 --> 36:27.180
Mr. Fang is here.

36:27.750 --> 36:29.100
He's Duke Pei's pupil.

36:30.790 --> 36:31.630
Look.

36:32.060 --> 36:33.430
So that is Mr. Fang.

36:38.090 --> 36:38.950
Mr. Fang.

36:38.950 --> 36:39.950
- Yeah.
- Mr. Fang.

36:39.950 --> 36:41.270
- Mr. Fang.
- Mr. Fang.

36:41.430 --> 36:42.270
Xu,

36:42.700 --> 36:43.990
it's Fang Xianye again.

36:44.220 --> 36:45.060
Mr. Fang.

36:45.730 --> 36:46.950
- Mr. Fang.
- Mr. Fang.

36:56.700 --> 36:59.350
Consort Yu is here.

37:04.910 --> 37:06.990
Greetings, Your Grace.

37:22.790 --> 37:23.870
- Prophet.
- Prophet.

37:33.700 --> 37:35.390
How I wish I could take off your mask.

37:36.990 --> 37:38.500
You have no taste, Great Ancestor.

37:39.390 --> 37:40.910
My peerless face

37:41.180 --> 37:43.140
has fascinated countless women.

37:44.540 --> 37:45.380
Spiritual energy.

37:45.660 --> 37:46.500
A spirit is here.

37:47.140 --> 37:48.540
It's coming this way, I think.

37:53.750 --> 37:54.620
Great Ancestor,

37:55.350 --> 37:56.540
my body reacts badly

37:57.540 --> 37:59.350
to all spirits but you.

38:01.140 --> 38:02.060
You go first.

38:02.060 --> 38:02.950
I'll look around.

38:14.580 --> 38:15.500
Your Highness,

38:15.500 --> 38:16.340
come with me, please.

38:28.350 --> 38:30.620
There's quite a crowd here today.

38:31.220 --> 38:32.660
Young ladies and gentlemen in town

38:32.660 --> 38:33.870
are gathering here.

38:34.390 --> 38:35.950
Even the Prophet has come.

38:36.750 --> 38:38.540
I'm so delighted.

38:40.310 --> 38:41.660
Make yourselves at home.

38:42.100 --> 38:43.500
If you find it boring,

38:43.830 --> 38:44.690
you can walk around

38:44.700 --> 38:46.350
in the garden of Linhua Palace.

38:46.790 --> 38:47.630
- Yes.
- Yes.

38:52.020 --> 38:52.860
Your Grace.

39:07.870 --> 39:08.710
Cheers, General Duan.

40:00.870 --> 40:02.830
How come he shielded my detection?

40:03.350 --> 40:04.790
Come on, ladies.

40:06.430 --> 40:07.270
Here you are.

40:07.910 --> 40:08.750
It tastes great.

40:15.990 --> 40:17.990
I'm too weak to sit for long.

40:17.990 --> 40:19.020
I want to take a walk.

40:19.350 --> 40:20.190
Please forgive me.

40:22.060 --> 40:23.020
As you wish, Prophet.

40:50.750 --> 40:51.590
Great Ancestor.

40:54.870 --> 40:56.700
Shortly after you left,

40:57.020 --> 40:57.950
the red spots on me

40:57.950 --> 40:58.830
all faded away.

40:59.390 --> 41:00.390
Have you caught him?

41:00.390 --> 41:01.230
What's he look like?

41:03.020 --> 41:04.020
He escaped.

41:04.470 --> 41:05.310
Escaped?

41:06.830 --> 41:07.790
He did that

41:07.790 --> 41:09.310
right under your nose?

41:09.700 --> 41:10.700
When I got there,

41:10.700 --> 41:11.790
he had escaped.

41:12.470 --> 41:13.700
I used my power to detect,

41:14.830 --> 41:16.270
but didn't find any trace.

41:17.220 --> 41:18.470
How did that happen?

41:19.270 --> 41:20.220
It doesn't make sense.

41:20.990 --> 41:22.790
He managed to shield your detection.

41:25.390 --> 41:26.230
Could it be...?

41:27.270 --> 41:28.110
It's Song Xingyu.

41:30.310 --> 41:31.180
Only the Glazed Pagoda

41:31.180 --> 41:32.060
he has been holding

41:32.620 --> 41:34.580
can shield your detection.

41:36.460 --> 41:37.300
It seems you aren't

41:37.310 --> 41:38.580
a very powerful prophet.

41:39.310 --> 41:41.100
He's been in the palace,

41:41.100 --> 41:42.270
but you haven't noticed.

41:43.540 --> 41:45.540
Even you can't find him.

41:45.950 --> 41:47.540
Don't give me a hard time.

41:54.990 --> 41:56.180
Take out your magical artifact

41:56.180 --> 41:57.020
to track spirits.

42:25.750 --> 42:26.990
I've set a formation here.

42:27.870 --> 42:28.990
Once he appears,

42:29.180 --> 42:30.350
I'll know.

42:31.580 --> 42:32.420
Then...

42:33.270 --> 42:35.220
You go on to search for obsessions.

42:36.540 --> 42:37.700
I'll take my leave.

42:48.180 --> 42:49.310
Sadly, my son

42:49.310 --> 42:51.390
is too busy to come today.

42:52.350 --> 42:53.790
Why don't the three of you stay here

42:53.790 --> 42:55.350
and have dinner with me?

42:56.060 --> 42:58.180
By then, Mingxuan will be back.

42:58.390 --> 42:59.310
I believe he also wants

42:59.310 --> 43:00.500
to meet you.

43:01.180 --> 43:02.040
It's my honor

43:02.040 --> 43:03.470
to have dinner with you

43:03.470 --> 43:04.540
and His Highness.

43:04.750 --> 43:06.100
The honor is mine too.

43:23.870 --> 43:24.870
I was away for too long.

43:25.100 --> 43:25.990
Since I came back,

43:26.350 --> 43:28.060
I haven't greeted you privately.

43:28.910 --> 43:30.270
Young Master Xu,

43:30.270 --> 43:31.220
you're a man of charm.

43:31.790 --> 43:32.660
It's so kind of you

43:33.100 --> 43:34.140
to say that.

43:35.870 --> 43:37.020
You flatter me, Your Grace.

43:37.790 --> 43:38.630
I've heard

43:38.790 --> 43:40.470
the garden in your palace

43:40.790 --> 43:42.060
was exquisitely crafted

43:42.430 --> 43:43.390
by folk craftsmen.

43:45.390 --> 43:46.230
Miss Wang.

43:47.470 --> 43:48.430
Would you like to go

43:48.660 --> 43:49.830
and appreciate it with me?

44:00.140 --> 44:01.020
Your Grace,

44:01.020 --> 44:02.470
I'm also curious.

44:03.020 --> 44:04.180
Please approve.

44:08.220 --> 44:10.100
I won't force you to stay then.

44:10.830 --> 44:11.750
You may leave.

44:13.700 --> 44:14.580
Thank you, Your Grace.

44:23.350 --> 44:24.270
This banquet

44:25.270 --> 44:26.620
is so boring.

44:28.830 --> 44:29.950
I'll sneak out soon

44:30.140 --> 44:30.980
and leave you alone.

44:46.430 --> 44:47.660
Go find the person

44:47.870 --> 44:48.990
with the strongest obsession.

44:57.960 --> 44:58.980
Thank you.

45:06.900 --> 45:07.740
No, no.

45:10.750 --> 45:12.870
How are your parents?

45:12.870 --> 45:13.790
They're very well.

45:13.950 --> 45:14.830
Thank you for caring.

45:15.910 --> 45:17.220
Come on, let's have a toast.

45:17.220 --> 45:18.270
Yes, Your Grace.

45:27.870 --> 45:29.580
Your art is impressive.

45:29.870 --> 45:31.180
I can't compare.

45:31.500 --> 45:32.430
Don't be so modest.

45:32.790 --> 45:33.630
Your needlework

45:33.830 --> 45:35.470
is far beyond my reach.

45:36.270 --> 45:37.540
Come to my home someday

45:37.540 --> 45:38.540
and we can practice.

45:39.390 --> 45:40.230
All right.

45:40.700 --> 45:41.870
Thank you

45:42.060 --> 45:43.020
for helping me out.

45:43.990 --> 45:44.910
After all,

45:45.540 --> 45:46.620
your awkward situation

45:46.910 --> 45:48.140
was my fault.

45:49.060 --> 45:49.950
I'm the one

45:49.950 --> 45:51.220
who should apologize.

45:52.660 --> 45:53.750
Born in this kind of family,

45:53.910 --> 45:55.270
you and I have no choice.

45:55.830 --> 45:56.830
We're both pawns.

45:57.020 --> 45:58.660
Let's not apologize for that.

46:00.870 --> 46:01.710
Miss Wang,

46:02.470 --> 46:03.540
don't be too pessimistic.

46:04.870 --> 46:05.710
Life is a chessboard.

46:06.660 --> 46:07.540
We're either a pawn

46:08.660 --> 46:09.500
or a player.

46:10.950 --> 46:11.790
I believe

46:12.660 --> 46:14.060
when we control the game,

46:14.700 --> 46:15.540
success or failure

46:15.870 --> 46:17.140
will lie in a decision we make.

46:39.220 --> 46:40.060
Miss Wang.

46:41.220 --> 46:42.340
- Watch out!
- Look out!

46:45.990 --> 46:46.830
Are you all right?

46:48.500 --> 46:49.390
Yes.

46:49.390 --> 46:50.430
Thank you, Mr. Fang.

46:53.750 --> 46:59.080
♪Between black and white,
ripples crossed♪

46:59.410 --> 47:03.660
♪Light encountered shadow♪

47:05.020 --> 47:07.270
♪Suddenly cracked♪

47:09.630 --> 47:12.790
♪Listen, all sounds are roaring♪

47:12.790 --> 47:15.320
♪As cold ice turns into tides♪

47:15.320 --> 47:20.840
♪A century's loneliness melts dreams♪

47:20.840 --> 47:24.080
♪Following fate's guidance♪

47:24.080 --> 47:28.940
♪By fate, our moments were exchanged♪

47:29.280 --> 47:32.300
♪The heart wakes up all of a sudden♪

47:33.801 --> 47:39.131
♪Between black and white,
ripples crossed♪

47:39.461 --> 47:43.711
♪Light encountered shadow♪

47:45.071 --> 47:50.441
♪It pierced the darkness and the time♪

47:50.741 --> 47:55.341
♪The unbreakable fate♪

47:56.431 --> 47:58.271
♪Suddenly cracked♪

48:10.481 --> 48:15.921
♪Between black and white,
ripples crossed♪

48:16.101 --> 48:20.431
♪Light encountered shadow♪

48:21.801 --> 48:27.191
♪It pierced the darkness and the time♪

48:27.421 --> 48:31.361
♪The unbreakable fate♪

48:33.131 --> 48:35.021
♪Suddenly cracked♪

48:37.681 --> 48:40.841
♪Listen, all sounds are roaring♪

48:40.841 --> 48:43.371
♪As cold ice turns into tides♪

48:43.371 --> 48:48.891
♪A century's loneliness melts dreams♪

48:48.891 --> 48:52.131
♪Following fate's guidance♪

48:52.131 --> 48:56.991
♪By fate, our moments were exchanged♪

48:57.331 --> 49:00.351
♪The heart wakes up all of a sudden♪

49:00.351 --> 49:03.171
♪Watch fireworks fall like stars♪

49:03.431 --> 49:05.961
♪This bond is tangled into a thread♪

49:05.961 --> 49:11.381
♪Worldly reflections fade into mist♪

49:11.551 --> 49:14.621
♪Borrowing one fleeting heartbeat♪

49:14.781 --> 49:19.681
♪You drew me into mortal dust,
till I'm enamored with its charms♪

49:19.891 --> 49:23.361
♪The heart wakes up all of a sudden♪
